										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There are many </span><b>free AI stock trading bots</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> available on the market. However, what strategies are commonly used when applying AI to stock trading? One common approach is to use AI for high-frequency or short-term trading. AI can execute trades quickly and consistently, which may reduce reliance on manual operations in high-frequency environments. This is one reason why some traders use AI stock trading bots and AI trading platforms. </span></p>
