<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In addition to identifying opportunities, AI trading bots also help manage risk. They can automatically set stop-loss and take-profit levels, control position sizes, and even stop trading once a daily loss limit is reached.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For day trading and automated stock trading, the biggest advantage of these tools is that they save time, improve execution efficiency, and make the entire trading process more disciplined.</span></p>
