					<description><![CDATA[<p>VAST Data has officially ascended to a $30 billion valuation. This comes after a massive $1 billion strategic injection led by NVIDIA.  This newly raised round triples VAST Data&#8217;s valuation</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/vast-data-hits-30b-valuation-with-nvidias-1b-boost/" data-wpel-link="internal">VAST Data Hits $30B Valuation with NVIDIA’s $1B Boost</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
