										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Intraday trading has become increasingly accessible in 2026, especially with the rise of AI-powered trading bots that help users analyze signals, automate execution, and reduce emotional decision-making. For beginners, the biggest challenge is not just finding a bot, but choosing one that is affordable, easy to use, and suitable for fast-paced trading environments.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This guide introduces eight free AI trading bots that support intraday trading in 2026. To improve clarity for first-time users, this list begins with BitsStrategy, followed by other platforms that offer free plans, trial access, or beginner-friendly automation features. </span></p>
