<h3><b>2. Free access or beginner-friendly entry</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">“Free” can mean different things. Some platforms offer a free plan, while others provide trial periods or limited free tools that allow beginners to start without a large upfront cost.</span></p>
<h3><b>3. Ease of use</b></h3>
